20:["$","section",null,{"className":"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl p-8","children":[["$","p",null,{"className":"text-white/70 leading-relaxed mb-6","children":"It is 2:17am on a Tuesday. Your phone rings — a homeowner in Manchester has a burst pipe flooding their kitchen. You are asleep, three rooms away, and the call goes to voicemail. By morning, they have already called another plumber who answered. That single missed call just cost you £280 in emergency callout fees plus a potential £800 rewiring job."}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-white/70 leading-relaxed mb-6","children":"This scenario plays out thousands of times every night across the UK. According to Office for National Statistics (ONS) data, 62% of calls to small UK trade businesses go unanswered — and that figure rises to 78% for calls made outside standard business hours (9am–5pm, Monday–Friday). For emergency trades, after-hours calls represent the highest-value enquiries: desperate customers with urgent problems who are willing to pay premium rates for immediate help."}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-white/70 leading-relaxed mb-6","children":["24/7 call answering has traditionally been the domain of large enterprises with dedicated night teams. But AI technology has democratised round-the-clock coverage. For ",["$","a",null,{"href":"/pricing","className":"text-emerald-400 hover:underline","children":"Starter plans from £59/month"}],", a sole trader can now offer the same 24/7 availability as a national firm — without hiring staff, without night shifts, and without the complexity of human rota management."]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-white/70 leading-relaxed mb-6","children":["This guide covers everything UK tradespeople need to know about 24/7 call answering in 2026: which trades need it most, how AI handles emergency calls at 2am, real cost comparisons against human services, ROI calculations, and step-by-step setup. Whether you are a ",["$","a",null,{"href":"/for-plumbers","className":"text-emerald-400 hover:underline","children":"plumber"}],", ",["$","a",null,{"href":"/for-locksmiths","className":"text-emerald-400 hover:underline","children":"locksmith"}],",",["$","a",null,{"href":"/for-heating-engineers","className":"text-emerald-400 hover:underline","children":"heating engineer"}],", ",["$","a",null,{"href":"/for-electricians","className":"text-emerald-400 hover:underline","children":"electrician"}],", or ",["$","a",null,{"href":"/for-roofers","className":"text-emerald-400 hover:underline","children":"emergency roofer"}],", this guide will show you how to capture every after-hours opportunity without sacrificing your sleep or personal life."]}],["$","p",null,{"className":"text-white/70 leading-relaxed","children":["For a broader overview of how AI call answering works across all trade scenarios, see our ",["$","a",null,{"href":"/blog/ai-call-answering-uk-tradespeople-definitive-guide-2026","className":"text-emerald-400 hover:underline","children":"complete guide to AI call answering"}],". To see how we stack up against the competition, read ",["$","a",null,{"href":"/blog/best-ai-call-answering-service-uk-trades-2026","className":"text-emerald-400 hover:underline","children":"how we compare to competitors"}],". Ready to stop missing calls? ",["$","a",null,{"href":"/","className":"text-emerald-400 hover:underline","children":"Start your free trial"}]," today."]}]]}]}]
