45:["$","p",null,{"className":"text-white/70 leading-relaxed mt-6","children":"Other trades that benefit significantly from 24/7 answering include drainage engineers, gas engineers, emergency glaziers, and appliance repair technicians. Even non-emergency trades like builders, painters, and kitchen fitters see value — weekend and evening enquiries are often when homeowners have time to plan projects, and being the first to respond can secure £5,000–£25,000 renovation contracts."}]
